text:
What else is possible?
These are just examples, not the only options.


&lt;div class="card-badge"&gt;Fancy 01&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Glassmorphism cards&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Soft transparency, blur, layered shadows, and subtle floating motion.&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;div class="card-badge"&gt;Fancy 02&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Shimmer loading effect&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A moving light sweep adds energy to cards, sections, or callouts.&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;div class="card-badge"&gt;Fancy 03&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Glow borders&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Animated gradient borders create a more premium, high-tech feel.&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;div class="card-badge"&gt;Fancy 04&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Orbital highlight&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A blurred glow rotates around the card to create a dynamic spotlight effect.&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;div class="card-badge"&gt;Fancy 05&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Gradient text + animated underline&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Great for hero titles, featured sections, or portfolio headers.&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;div class="card-badge"&gt;Fancy 06&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Staggered entrance system&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Multiple items appear one after another for a more designed presentation flow.&lt;/p&gt;
